HeaderInfo - Class in com.biorecorder.edflib
This class allows to store the information required to create EDF/BDF file header and correctly extract data from Data Records.
HeaderInfo(FileType) - Constructor for class com.biorecorder.edflib.HeaderInfo
Default constructor that creates a HeaderInfo instance with 0 channels (signals).
HeaderInfo(int, FileType) - Constructor for class com.biorecorder.edflib.HeaderInfo
This constructor creates a HeaderInfo instance of the given type (EDF_16BIT or BDF_24BIT) with the given number of channels (signals)

HeaderInfo(File) - Constructor for class com.biorecorder.edflib.HeaderInfo
